<% title = 'OpenMRS ID - '+user[conf.user.displayname] %>
<% name = 'root' %>
<% headline = 'Welcome to the Dashboard, '+user[conf.user.displayname]+'.' %>
<% if (user.memberof.indexOf('dashboard-administrators') > -1) { sidebar = ['./../views/sidebar/crowd'] } %>

<p><h2>New to the OpenMRS Community?</h2>
Welcome, we're glad you joined us! If you haven't already, you should complete the following steps to let others know who you are:
<ol>
	<li><a href="/mailinglists">Subscribe to a Mailing List</a> and stay connected to the community.</li>
	<li><a href="https://wiki.openmrs.org/users/editmyprofile.action">Edit your Wiki Profile</a> so we can learn more about you.</li>
	<li><a href="http://wiki.openmrs.org/spaces/createpersonalspace.action">Create your own Personal Space</a> on the Wiki.</li>
</ol>
</p>

